<H1>
<FONT COLOR="#000080" FACE="VERDANA,ARIAL,HELVETICA,HELV,GENEVA">
 
</FONT>
</H1>
<P><P>
<A NAME="seminar"></A><P>

<A NAME="511869"></A>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#000080" FACE="VERDANA,ARIAL,HELVETICA,HELV,GENEVA"><B>
 FREE Educational Seminars throughout Europe-- Turn Your Call Center into a Competitive Weapon 
</B></FONT>
</H2>

Discover how today's advanced call center technology is helping companies provide personalized, one-on-one customer care. This half-day session will focus on customer care business issues specific to call center managers in a number of industries, and the critical role that call centers play, not only in customer retention, but in customer acquisition and the ability to sell additional services into the existing customer base. <P>
Sign up now for the Call Center Technology Forum nearest you: London- Nov 4, Paris - Nov 6, Amsterdam - Nov 11, Frankfurst - Nov 12, Milan - Nov 13.<P>

<UL>
	<LI><a href="http://www.wwem.com/scopus.html"><FONT COLOR="#000080" FACE="VERDANA,ARIAL,HELVETICA,HELV,GENEVA"><B>More information</B></FONT></a></LI>
	<LI><a href="http://www.wwem.com/scopus.html"><FONT COLOR="#000080" FACE="VERDANA,ARIAL,HELVETICA,HELV,GENEVA"><B>Register Here</B></FONT></a></LI>
</UL>

